Class GenericDataSink

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.common.operators.Operator<org.apache.flink.types.Nothing>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.flink.util.Visitable<org.apache.flink.api.common.operators.Operator<?>>

    public class GenericDataSink
extends org.apache.flink.api.common.operators.base.GenericDataSinkBase<org.apache.flink.types.Record>
    Operator for nodes that act as data sinks, storing the data they receive. The way the data is stored is handled by the OutputFormat.
